UX & UI Design Â· 2015
Role in project: UX Design, UI Design, Front-end web development
Work on Bom Squad included graphic design, user interface design and user experience design on their bill of materials online tool.
For the graphic design, this included a new logo, colour palette, typography work. The user interface included all of the above, well as email template and menu reoganization - all detailed in a thirty-four page style guide. User experience work included running usability tests, as well as re-working the onboarding flow to help new customers understand the system.
